es not\nobserved previously. We also solve an open problem of Kopparty and Rossman on\nthe homomorphism domination exponent of paths. One of our main tools is\ntropicalization, a well-known technique in complex algebraic geometry. We prove\nseveral results about tropicalizations which may be of independent interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2021 20:02:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 18:08:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-03"}
